<doc id="55838" wikidata="Q1208838" url="?curid=55838" title="National Security Act">
<text>National Security Act may refer to:
*National Security Act (India), law to provide for preventive detention
*National Security Act (South Korea), regarding seditious activities
*National Security Act of 1947, a United States law that established the Central Intelligence Agency
*National Security Act 2017 (Canada)
*National Security Act 2023, a UK act strengthening laws against espionage, political interference, sabotage, and assassination

National Security Law may refer to:
*National Security Law of the United States
*National Security Law of the People&#x27;s Republic of China
**Macau national security law
**Hong Kong national security law
*National Security Law (Brazil)

